# Google Maps API key with the "Map Tiles API" enabled.
# Without this, the 3D campus walker (/universities/:id/explore) still loads
# but shows a flat placeholder ground instead of photorealistic Melbourne.
# Get a key: https://console.cloud.google.com → APIs → Map Tiles API
# Restrict the key to your domain in production.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
